@node Main "Pwaps - Documentation"

                               'Pwaps' 1.0

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Pwaps' is a Workbench @{" game " link play} that is played in a diamond shaped
board, the goal is to put as many tiles of the same type together as
possible. When at least 2 tiles of the same type are placed next to
each other, they are then removed from the board and replaced by new
tiles.

  Have fun!

